map_npcs.name: Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Probably best that you don't go in there for now...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Hmmm, we're getting some strange readings from within this cave.

map_npcs.name: Impatient Researcher
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Gah, I wish the construction team would let me know what's going on in there...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Hey, wait your turn, I was here first!

map_npcs.name: Professor Lyra
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Have you spoken with David yet? He's near the tents.
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, hello there, you must be {player}! It's so nice to be meeting you!
Now, I know there's a lot to adjust to, there's plenty of time for that.
I'm Lyra, the head researcher of this humble Hub.
If you'll speak with David, he'll be able to help you get your ID.{objective:Meet David near the tents.}

map_npcs.name: Researcher David
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Can't talk right now, I'm busy...
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Go away, I'm busy, and I don't have time to talk.
...
Wait a sec, you're one of those two new contractors, yeah?
Take, this and go talk to Lyra again, I'm still going to be busy for a bit here.{objective:Return to Professor Lyra}

map_npcs.name: Professor Lyra
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Please go interact with the Safe Save Station. I'll be here when you're done!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Oh, perfect, you have your ID, a couple last things before you're ready to be on your way!
Try standing on the blue glowing square! It's an Oochcorp patented Save Station and provides many useful features, such as the ability to use the Oochabox!
The Oochabox is handy storage system that allows you to store and grab more than your standard team of 4 Oochamon, and you can access it while standing on a teleporter and using the menu!
Let me know once you've done so!{objective:Interact with the Save Station.}

map_npcs.name: Professor Lyra
map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Please stay safe, you're always welcome to return when you need to!
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue:
Ah, yes, your first task.
There's word that one of our lovely researchers has- ***BOOM***
Oh my word, what was that?!
I have a new request for you, would you please check on whatever made that awful noise?{objective:Investigate the Impact.}
The impact sounds like it came from somewhere just to the northwest of the Hub's Entrance!
Oh, and where are my manners, I've been meaning to give you these!

Behave yourself, wouldn't want to have to toss ya in the brig.

map_npcs.name: Guard George
map_npcs.pre_combat_dialogue: Oh, hi, you can enter and leave freely now!

Ah, I'm glad you've made it back safely.
Some of our top researchers are investigating the happenings in the caves you just explored.
Rest assured, we will get to the bottom of this.
Now, once you're all rested up, head up through the caves once more.
The team working at the Lava Settlement could really use a hand as well.{objective:Re-enter the caves and travel north to the Lava Settlement}
Oh, and please take these.

map_npcs.post_combat_dialogue: Guess I'll go back to the Shop to buy some more...
